Description:  This package provides the Boost v1.81.0 libraries.
 Boost is a set of free, peer-reviewed, portable C++ source libraries.
 
 This package provides the following run-time libraries:
 - atomic
 - chrono
 - container
 - context
 - contract
 - coroutine and coroutine2 (Coroutine is deprecated - use Coroutine2)
 - date_time
 - exception
 - filesystem
 - fiber
 - graph
 - - graph-parallel
 - iostreams
 - json
 - locale
 - log
 - math
 - nowide
 - program_options
 - python3
 - random
 - regex
 - serialization and wserialization
 - stackstrace
 - system
 - thread
 - timer
 - type_erasure
 - url (new)
 - wave
 
 There are many more header-only libraries supported by Boost.
 See more at http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_81_0/

